# Design system (DESIGN.md)

Authoritative visual spec: [`DESIGN.md`](../../DESIGN.md). Tokens live in [`packages/ui/src/styles/globals.css`](../../packages/ui/src/styles/globals.css). Components: `@repo/ui/components/*`.

## Palette

- **Primary CTA:** emerald `#3ecf8e` (`bg-primary` / `bg-brand-primary`). Use sparingly ‚Äî one filled green button per viewport when possible.
- **Text on primary:** near-black `#171717` (`text-primary-foreground` / `text-ink`) ‚Äî **never white** on emerald.
- **Pressed primary:** `#24b47e` (`bg-brand-primary-deep`).
- **Canvas:** white `#ffffff` (`bg-background`). Soft bands: `#fafafa` (`bg-canvas-soft` / `bg-muted`).
- **Ink ladder:** `text-foreground` / `text-ink` ‚Üí `text-ink-mute` ‚Üí `text-ink-mute-2` ‚Üí `text-ink-faint`.
- **Borders:** `border-hairline` / `border-border` (`#dfdfdf`); emphasis `border-hairline-strong`.
- **Dark surfaces:** `bg-canvas-night` / `.dark` for code blocks and featured dark cards ‚Äî not atmospheric marketing gradients.
- **Do not** introduce purple, pink, yellow, or indigo as system/UI colors (charts/logos only).

## Typography

- **UI / display:** Inter via `--font-inter` (`font-sans`, `font-heading`). Weights **400** body, **500** display/headings ‚Äî never 600+ for display.
- **Code:** `font-mono` (Geist Mono).
- Display utilities: `text-display-xxl` ‚Ä¶ `text-display-md`, `text-heading-lg`, `text-body-md`, `text-button-md`, `text-micro`.

## Shape & components

- **Buttons:** `rounded-sm` (6px) ‚Äî square-ish, **never** pill-shaped.
- **Inputs:** `rounded-sm`, hairline border, padding ~8√ó12.
- **Cards:** `rounded-lg` (12px), flat + 1px hairline (no heavy shadow by default).
- **Pills/badges:** `rounded-full` is OK for tags only.
- Prefer `@repo/ui` primitives (`Button`, `Input`, `Card`, `Badge`) over custom colored markup.
- Use semantic tokens (`bg-primary`, `text-muted-foreground`) ‚Äî not raw `bg-green-500` / `zinc-*` for brand UI.

## Don'ts

- No atmospheric gradients on heroes ‚Äî white canvas is the design.
- No white text on emerald buttons.
- No pill-shaped primary buttons.
- No extra brand accent colors as system tokens.
